minaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/khuluq-islam-al-haya\/","url_meta":{"origin":5910,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Islam is characterized by modesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, every religion has a character and the character of Islam is modesty.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4182 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":107,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2010\/11\/10\/modesty-is-part-of-faith\/","url_meta":{"origin":5910,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Modesty: Do not admonish him, modesty is part of faith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 10, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by a man from the Ansar who was warning his brother about modesty, but the Prophet said, \u201cLet him be, for modesty is part of faith.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 24, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 36 Grade:\u00a0Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26202,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/04\/13\/dua-allah-shy-empty-handed\/","url_meta":{"origin":5910,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Allah shy to turn away a sincere prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 13, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Salman al-Farsi reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is conscientious and generous. He would be shy, when a man raises his hands to Him, to turn them away empty and disappointed.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3556 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0627\u0631\u0650\u0633\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17151,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/12\/haya-jannah-badha-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":5910,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Haya: Modesty in Paradise, shamelessness in Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 12, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cModesty is part of faith and faith is in Paradise. Shamelessness is part of insolence and insolence is in Hellfire.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2009 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32079,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/14\/entire-deen-haya\/","url_meta":{"origin":5910,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Haya: All of Islam revolves around modesty","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 14, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Qurrah ibn Iyas reported: We were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, when modesty was mentioned to him. They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, is modesty part of the religion?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cRather, it is the entire religion.\u201d Then, the Prophet said, \u201cVerily, modesty,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13827,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/30\/hayaa-modesty-shyness\/","url_meta":{"origin":5910,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Modesty: Healthy shame, conscience bring all goodness","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Imran ibn Husayn reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cModesty does not bring anything but\u00a0goodness.\u201d In another narration, the Prophet said, \"Modesty is good in all things.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6117, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 37 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u0650\u0645\u0652\u0631\u064